4/23/14: at Harbor 25 years ago, then Star Linen for ~17 years, then back to Harbor 8-9 yrs ago.  Moved over to help Jonathan with gov't projects but still has some nursing home accounts.
Product Specialist.  Window, Bedding, & Cubicle Treatments

6/4/14:
1) Parents getting older, still living in his home state of Ohio.  Sister is nearby to help care for them.
2) Son is still doing well.  Living in Colorado but just got a place in Puerto Rico as well.  He owns a successful business that owns/leases ATM machines.  Might sell it so that he can focus on music.  His band, Airtight Experiment, is online.  From previous marriage so ~20 year gap b/t him and daughter.
3) 16-year old daughter, 3 more years of high school but she will probably attend college nearby as well since she enjoys the area and is very involved with their horses.
from Massachusetts originally (b/t Boston and Providence) but has been in Savannah for 24 years.
